Hi @{5a784a852aa9952cbfa59813}, I see you're going through the [Intermediate: Upload Velodyne Model](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?cat=guided_i&tut=guided_i4) tutorial! Congrats on making the pull request! Even though, as the description says, you shouldn't have :wink: As the name of your branch (`velodyne_tutorial_do_not_merge`) suggests, this pull request won't be merged because that model already exists in the database.

Now that you understand the process of contributing models, we welcome contributions of your original creations in the future! Please check the tutorial on [How to contribute a model](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?tut=model_contrib&cat=build_robot) for more detailed information :)
